# Tri-Engine Architecture: Canvas 2D, WebGL & WebGPU

We will completely separate the architectures into three distinct engines in `src_demo`: **Canvas 2D (Lightweight Charts)**, **WebGL (PixiJS)**, and a new **WebGPU (PixiJS v8 / Native WGSL)** engine. We will implement native drawing tools and indicators for each engine in its respective native language, ensuring peak performance. Finally, we will build a universal bridge between all three engines so data is perfectly preserved when toggling between them via a 3-way switch.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a major architectural overhaul. We will do this **strictly in `src_demo`** so your original `src` remains completely untouched and safe. We will use `src` only as a reference for your original logic.

